    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 B32 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains composed thanks to documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry featuring polyurethane bushings. Recent VANOS overhaul and a comprehensive valve shim adjustment ensure the valvetrain operates within strict factory tolerances. Equipped with a torque-sensing limited-slip differential and M-spec cross-drilled rotors, this example provides the mechanical transparency and high-revving engagement that defines the peak of the analog driving era.",
      "price": 34500.0,
